name: Sprint UI - Design System Generator
description:
Sprint UI is a design system generator that helps you customise a base design system within minutes. Every change you make using the plugin will automatically update every component of your design.


Packed with:

  • 700+ resizable components,
  • 900+ icons and your typography
  • Colour guide sorted out (5 colour shades)


Visit sprintui.com to create a Sprint UI account to start generating design systems.
